commit.message:
Support variable release prefix lengths (#467)

* Prototype variable release prefix lengths

Prototype allowing for a variable number of parts for a release label prefix to support the scenario of not moving between .NET preview releases.

* Add --pre-release-label argument

Add new `--pre-release-label` argument to control filtering of pre-release packages.
